{"type": "article", "id": 23527, "title": "带三角金属支撑的书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103908dZ6N7Uimn1CrDwV4.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个书架来自纽约布鲁克林的工作室 Souda，由一家线上设计网站 WorkOf 出售。它使用金属三脚架做支撑固定在墙上，一块浅色的木板横亘在其中，恰好在中间的位置，使得书架维持了中心对称。因为模块化的设计，可以在墙上排列多个架子构成一面书架，很灵活。有 6 种颜色和 3 种材料的木板可选，售价 350 美元起，<a href=\"http://workof.com/p/strut-shelving-system-copper/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103905Qamte5o6guJTqMkR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103905UKrZaOxmGcEqSsRI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103906ONBDbjqJMia72pRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103907Lc7EtMpYOFzbBSDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103908hAuJRvpUsVlPMtDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}